### Job Tag Controller Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags

### 1. Create a new Job Tag - Remote
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Remote"
}

### 2. Create Job Tag - Urgent
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Urgent"
}

### 3. Create Job Tag - Startup
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Startup"
}

### 4. Create Job Tag - Fortune500
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fortune500"
}

### 5. Create Job Tag - Benefits
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Benefits"
}

### 6. Create Job Tag - Visa Sponsorship
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Visa Sponsorship"
}

### 7. Get all Job Tags
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags

### 8. Get Job Tag by ID (1)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/1

### 9. Get Job Tag by ID (2)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/2

### 10. Get Job Tag by ID (3)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/3

### 11. Get Job Tag by ID (4)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/4

### 12. Get Job Tag by ID (5)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/5

### 13. Update Job Tag (1) - Remote to Remote-Friendly
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Remote-Friendly"
}

### 14. Update Job Tag (2) - Urgent to High Priority
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "High Priority"
}

### 15. Update Job Tag (3) - Startup to Early Stage Startup
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Early Stage Startup"
}

### 16. Delete Job Tag (6)
DELETE http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/6

### 17. Get all Job Tags after deletion
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags

### 18. Try to get deleted tag (should fail)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/6

### 19. Try to create duplicate tag (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Remote-Friendly"
}

### 20. Try to update to duplicate name (should fail)
PUT http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Remote-Friendly"
}

### 21. Try to create tag without name (should fail)
POST http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### 22. Try to get non-existent tag (should fail)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/v1/job-tags/999
